{"tid":1910313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【RIP】Bossini創辦人孫女韓國抽脂後亡 丈夫於港入稟告整容診所","createTime":"2020-03-04T14:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T15:49:18.000Z","uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"de206acfd453bd43caebb707936f5b044e11575e","tid":1910313,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:42:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1583310242938&amp;issue=20200304\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1583310242938%26issue%3D20200304&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=741543f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1583310242938&amp;issue=20200304</a><br />\n【RIP】Bossini創辦人孫女韓國抽脂後亡 丈夫於港入稟告整容診所<br />\n文章日期：2020年3月4日 15:49<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200304/s00010/6e68b763d68c64ceb1ce815f1da17b9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200304%2Fs00010%2F6e68b763d68c64ceb1ce815f1da17b9a.jpg&h=17826c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - <br />\nBossini創辦人孫女韓國抽脂後亡 丈夫於港入稟告整容診所(網上圖片/資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n一名34歲香港女子於今年初於南韓一間整形外科醫院抽脂後死亡。《南華早報》報道，女死者為「針織大王」、堡獅龍（Bossini）創辦人羅定邦的孫女羅貝兒（Law Bonnie Evita）。<br />\n<br />\n其丈夫Danny Chi接受該報訪問時指，妻子在手術中被兩次注射俗稱「K仔」、「藍精靈」在內的強度鎮靜劑，惟疑手術前未做相關藥物測試。Danny Chi表示，妻子的死是「不幸、不必要的及非法」，全因診所疏忽、貪婪及無能所致。<br />\n<br />\nDanny Chi今日於香港法院入稟控告涉事的整形外科診所，兩名醫生及一名護士誤殺及偽造文件等罪名。"},{"pid":"ac6cada729d29757e9db3d02f08a90bac37de0ab","tid":1910313,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"RIP<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【夠鐘上Twitter啦喂！】大量英美議員需要人推！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1910266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1910266</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">夠鐘做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大量議員tweet唔夠人</span>"},{"pid":"dfe2b78fbfe859523f4664809f423499d136cd5f","tid":1910313,"uid":170979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:50:29.000Z","msg":"係咪之前比人綁架果個？"},{"pid":"037430e8df7c7f8e77dabd61cc7941920f5d21e1","tid":1910313,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"好肥咩?"},{"pid":"9f36239e1a63932c256dc35f4c66c61121951ab9","tid":1910313,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"香港法院管到?"},{"pid":"7913cfa3100aa5d764a95a50d478a750f9e7a71c","tid":1910313,"uid":93112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"iuissoq"},{"pid":"1371a82042463be24fc57eff4af49201b3be7525","tid":1910313,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:53:10.000Z","msg":"有咩photoshop搞唔掂要去抽脂"},{"pid":"dfafe1a6962335744dbee866269afe94fe39d2a9","tid":1910313,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7913cfa3100aa5d764a95a50d478a750f9e7a71c","tid":1910313,"uid":93112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"iuissoq"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"用感嘆號"},{"pid":"9c27104bc0194f36329cad7bc0c9124474c73c3b","tid":1910313,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1371a82042463be24fc57eff4af49201b3be7525","tid":1910313,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T14:53:10.000Z","msg":"有咩photoshop搞唔掂要去抽脂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:03:28.000Z","msg":"真人邊有得用ps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bd6ed4cfc803b88d85d9ef1b1b2d03f15bc86f","tid":1910313,"uid":275885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T15:49:18.000Z","msg":"可以喺香港告韓國架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}